## File tree — top 2 levels of apps/ and libs/

```
apps/
├── api/src/app/
│   ├── <module>/  — <one-line purpose>
│   └── ...
└── client/src/
    ├── pages/     — <if using react-router, list top-level page components>
    ├── components/
    ├── hooks/
    └── ...

libs/
├── domain/
│   ├── <feature>/  — <one-line purpose>
│   └── ...
├── backend/
│   └── core/       — <one-line purpose>
└── shared/
    ├── types/      — Zod schemas (single source of truth)
    ├── ui/         — shared React components
    └── utils/      — cross-cutting utilities
```

